reviews.text: Above average food and reasonable price. Good deal.

A great Cantonese restaurant located in the Harbour Plaza Resort City, part of the mall. We had lunch there and the food is awesome, so are the price range they offer the dishes. Very inexpensive.  Mind you it is important and wise to go there with a person who speaks and reads Chinese, nothing is printed in English.
Food not look exactly like photo but still taste great 👍👏👌
Came for family dinner. Reasonable price but very limited food to choose from the menu. Food was just fair and this resturant is not entitled for the mall parking.

reviews.text: Good location, clean, good price

love this place for shopping. Great to walk around if there's nothing else to do after all those tourity areas nearby. They renovated some outdoor terrace area and now it has a nice view of the ship and skyline.
Nice scenery, but price is bit high
Our fave Hotel at Hong Kong.. According to its locations and everything around it

A room with a view.  We stayed here then got the bus to HK city in less than 40 mins.  Located in the new territories it is less hectic than HK with lots of parks, malls and great transport links. The room was more of a suite with a separate seating area and bath. Ideal for getting over the jet lag.
